HEADWORD: Cliental
<hw>Cli*en"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
a client.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A dependent and <qex>cliental</qex> relation.</q>
<rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I sat down in the <qex>cliental</qex> chair.</q>
<rj><qau>Dickens.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cliented</ent>⟦br⟧
